In `app/_layout.tsx`, the `post-gig` Stack.Screen has `headerShown: false`. This means the screen has NO back button on Android (hardware back button still works, but there's no visual back button). This is fine for UX but confirm it's intentional.

More importantly: ensure the `post-gig` screen in `_layout.tsx` does NOT have `gestureEnabled: false` or any option that would prevent dismissal.

